<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.215859>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Fergusobia porosae n. sp. (all in lateral view): A, Entire parthenogenetic female; B, Head of parthenogenetic female; C, Habitus of parthenogenetic female; D, Tails of parthenogenetic females; E, Entire infective female; F, Head of infective female; G; Habitus of infective female; H, Tails of infective females; I, Entire male; J, Head of male; K, Habitus of males; L, Tails of males. Scale bars: A, E, I = 50 Μm. B, F, J = 5 Μm. C, D, G, H, K, L not drawn to scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/215859/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.215860>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Habitus drawings of Fergusobia spp. (most undescribed) collected from flat leaf galls: A, from E. albens; B, F. microcarpae n. sp. from E. microcarpa; C, from E. odorata; D, F. po ros a e sp. nov from E. porosa; E, F. fisheri from E. leucoxylon; F, from E. siderophloia; G, from C. intermedia; H, from Eucalyptus sp. from Brisbane; I, from Eucalyptus sp. from Lake Tinnaroo. Scale bars = 50 Μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/215860/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

